        <item>
            <title>Version 1.0.22+23</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <h1>Release notes - 1.0.22+23</h1>

                <h2>Features:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Added pause menu to the dashboard alongside updated tooltips..</li>
                    <li>Updated behavior of browser tracking for Windows, improved stability.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Fixes:</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Now activity no longer bound by fragments size. This should remove overflows.</li>
                    <li>Fixed "No activities" being shown first before actual data loads.</li>
                    <li>Fixed cache tile changing size in settings page.</li>
                    <li>Fixed statistics not showing last day in week/month views.</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
